column5: This is how I feel!!!    Thanks again to everyone who made my day today!!  Cool vid eh!!
When YOUR happy TJ, were all happy

After watchin the video and TJ sayin this is how his day went---was'nt sure if his day was good or not.  After all that elk was'nt sure if he wanted to wash his feet or not-----Man I hate when that happens.  Bushart
Yeah, seen that before not to long ago. One of our Biology instructors was using it to demonstrate unusual animal behavior, and challenging the students to try to figure out what it was doing.
I'd say he was stompin' the dude who shot his Ma! He was doin' the stomp.  And that right there is your feel good clip of the year.
Reminds me of the guy who recently posted a video of himself playing in the water with his "liftime socks". Oh happy days.
Cool video TJ Thanks for sharing your feelings with us Leechman
At the end of that I was waiting for it to come back and do a cannon ball
Can we switch up that elk for a couple of women in bikini's? That's a 'feel good' scenario too.

it was trying to cool down ...normally after this episode they roll in the mud...i raised elk and new zeland reds all through the 90s...this was a common site in the spring...when they are shedding their winter coats..  And yes you can never get bored of seeing this .....or the bulls when they do battle in the fall
